a town scryer shouted that it was time to cleanse karana from the evil plague.. so i decided to move there,When i zoned to karana i saw Braziers of Rodcet Nife's near búildings when i was heading towards the millers. When i came to the miller house Velarte Selire was there asking me if i have come to help against the plague, i then told him i was...after a few ppl were gatherd he explain what we had to do..he then handed out smudge stick's that we were gonna give to the Braziers of Rodcet nife and after you handed em they became a Filled Brazier like Halo posted...and after we filled all Braziers up he told us to gather and he Picked 4 of the 20 that was there, Me,Benpus,Brunix and one other sorry for forgeting your name... after that he told Benpus Brunix and the third person to hold hands while i was gonna stand behind him,after they had gatherd their hands he explained to me that i was the one that had been choosen to Light up the braziers in Rodcent nife's name and he gave me the Charcold of Rodcent nife, after i turned in the charcold to the Filled Brazier a Voice began to speak (will try to get Screenshots of this forgot to take some) and then the land began to heal itself and Velarte Selerin said that the plague was gone and no evil was left....<br>
